content: Cody Neiman is a student of Cocoa Beach Junior/Senior High School currently working as an Information Security Intern at the Kennedy Space Center (NASA) in Cape Canaveral, Florida. He is actively seeking an International Baccalaureate (IB) Diploma while developing his knowledge on Information Systems himself.
